steps.instruction:
1. Shred apples into large bowl using a coarse grater
2. Squeeze lemon for juice (2 tablespoons)
3. Add to apple and toss to coat
4. Stir in green onions and sauce until blended.
5. Chop broccoli finely
6. Add to apple mix and toss until blended
7. Chill 15 minutes. Toss before serving.

ingredients.note: Like Honeycrisp, Granny Smith or Fuji
